yum install docker -y
systemctl start docker
systemctl enable docker
Copy ubuntu image pull and paste in terminal
copy httpd image pull and paste in terminal
docker run -it --name devops docker pull ubuntu:rolling
inside container:
apt update -y
apt install apache2 -y
cd /var/www/html
cat > index.html
service apache2 start
service apache2 status
Create another tab for terminal:
docker ps -a
docker inspect devops | less(to get ip )
curl http://ip
Now we have to create another container:
docker run -it --name devops1 -p 8080:80 ubuntu:rolling /bin/bash
do everything again in that container
copy public ip from instance and do :8080
